<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<pipeline name="Photo-z Compute">
  <info>
    <group value="data_preparation"/>

    <owner value="ogando"/>
    <description>This pipeline computes photo-z for diffent algorithms.</description>
  </info>
  <taskgroup id="data_partitioning" desc="Data Partitioning">
    <task checked="checked" name="Trainings Separation" flow="1to1" confName="Trainings Separation" config="no" id="photoz_separate">
      <components>
        <component id="photoz_separate" name="Trainings Separation"/>
      </components>
      <dependencies>
        <dependency id="scienceportal">
          <file mimetype="text/xml" source="scienceportal" class="pype_input" value="pype_input.xml"/>
        </dependency>
      </dependencies>
    </task>
    <task checked="checked" name="Data Partitioning" flow="1toN" confName="Data Partitioning" config="yes" id="data_partitioning">
      <components>
        <component id="fileorganizer" name="Hadoop FS"/>
      </components>
      <dependencies>
        <dependency id="scienceportal">
          <file mimetype="text/xml" source="scienceportal" class="pype_input" value="pype_input.xml"/>
        </dependency>
      </dependencies>
    </task>
  </taskgroup>
  <taskgroup id="photoz" desc="Photo-z">
    <task checked="" name="ANNz" confName="Photometric Redshift" version="001" config="no" id="annz">
      <components>
        <component multithreaded="True" name="ANNz" id="annz"/>
      </components>
      <dependencies>
        <dependency id="photoz_separate">
          <file mimetype="application/x-tar" optional="True" class="training/annz"/>
          <config type="string" optional="True" id="photo_type_annz"/>
          <config type="string" optional="True" id="t_set"/>
          <config type="string" optional="True" id="n_inputs"/>
          <config type="string" optional="True" id="zp_corr_type"/>
          <config type="string" optional="True" id="zeropoint_table"/>
        </dependency>
        <dependency id="data_partitioning">
          <file mimetype="application/python-pickle" optional="False" class="science"/>
        </dependency>
      </dependencies>
    </task>
    <task checked="" name="ANNz2" confName="Photometric Redshift" version="001" config="no" id="annz2">

        <component multithreaded="True" name="ANNz2" id="annz2"/>
